longBusinessSummary: Publichnoye aktsionernoye obshchestvo "Stavropol'energosbyt" supplies electricity in the Stavropol territory, Russia. It is also involved in the production of steam and hot water. The company was founded in 2005 and is based in Essentuki, Russia.
